      "id": "a6e91938510a84f6c89678a479d01dd4d8ca8aa2",
      "message": "Remove the Value_Type.expect methods in favour of a new Checks module (#14899)\n\n- Removed `expect_*` from `Value_Type`.\n- Replaced with a new module `Standard.Table.Internal.Value_Type_Checks` with static methods `is_*` or `has_*` which error if not matching.\n- Removed `check_binary_boolean_op` and `check_binary_numeric_op` from `Value_Type_Helpers`.\n- Privatised `Standard.Database.Internal.Helpers`.\n- Replaced `expect_specific_integer_type` with `is_specific_integer_type` following the same rules as above.\n- Replaced `assume_default_locale` with `check_default_locale`, which errors if not default.",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-23T20:24:20Z",
      "author": {
        "name": "James Dunkerley"
      }
    }
